  const BUILT_IN_OBJECTS = [

  };

  const LITERALS = [

  const KEYWORDS = [

    "class_terminate",
    "default",
    "preserve",
    "in",
    "me",
    "byval",
    "byref",
    "step",
    "resume",
    "goto"
  ];

  return {
    name: 'VBScript',
    aliases: [ 'vbs' ],
    case_insensitive: true,
    keywords: {
      keyword: KEYWORDS,
      built_in: BUILT_IN_OBJECTS,
      literal: LITERALS
    },
    illegal: '//',
    contains: [
      BUILT_IN_CALL,
      hljs.inherit(hljs.QUOTE_STRING_MODE, { contains: [ { begin: '""' } ] }),
      hljs.COMMENT(
        /'/,
        /$/,
        { relevance: 0 }
      ),
      hljs.C_NUMBER_MODE
    ]
  };
}

module.exports = vbscript;
